Class MathMLCompiler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sbml.jsbml.util.compilers.MathMLCompiler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ASTNodeCompiler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HTMLFormula

    public class MathMLCompiler
extends java.lang.Object
implements ASTNodeCompiler
    With this compiler, an ASTNode can be transformed into a MathML string.
